## 基础用法
::TuffCodeBlock{lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TuffProgress :percentage="60" />
    <TuffProgress :percentage="60" :show-text="false" />
  </template>
---
::

## API（简版）
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: percentage
    type: 'number'
    default: '0'
    description: '进度百分比'
  - name: status
    type: "'success' | 'warning' | 'error'"
    default: '-'
    description: '状态色'
  - name: indeterminate
    type: 'boolean'
    default: 'false'
    description: '不确定进度'
---
::

